latestPosts.caption:
Finally tried @thepizzabaron38th in Tokyo and it was incredible ! 🍕 
Ranked No.1 in Asia and No.3 in the world — and I totally get why. It’s  a pizza omakase, so each slice was different and full of surprises.They mix Japanese flavors with classic Italian pizza, and it works so well. The dough was soft, airy, and perfectly crispy.
One of the best pizzas I’ve ever had.
If you’re in Tokyo, don’t miss this! Thank you @azuraholidays for this wonderful experience 🫰🏻
📍 The Pizza Bar on 38th, Mandarin Oriental Tokyo
